# TypeScript & Next.js Standards

## TypeScript Konfiguration:

- Hauptkonfiguration: [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json)
- Next.js spezifische Typen: [next-env.d.ts](mdc:next-env.d.ts)

## Code Standards:

- Verwende strikte TypeScript-Konfiguration
- Generiere Payload-Typen automatisch in [src/payload-types.ts](mdc:src/payload-types.ts)
- Verwende semicolons am Ende von Statements

## Next.js App Router:

- Struktur: [src/app/](mdc:src/app/) mit Route Groups
- Frontend: `(frontend)` Route Group
- Payload Admin: `(payload)` Route Group

## ESLint:

- Konfiguration: [eslint.config.mjs](mdc:eslint.config.mjs)
- Führe `npm run lint` vor Commits aus

## Testing:

- Vitest Konfiguration: [vitest.config.mts](mdc:vitest.config.mts)
- Playwright für E2E: [playwright.config.ts](mdc:playwright.config.ts)
